"perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909974}, {"id": 156677, "content": "为了结婚而谈恋爱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855998}, {"id": 156933, "content": "打撸不打王者", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903713}, {"id": 164869, "content": "很喜欢古代的东西，风俗啊，衣饰啊，建筑啊，文化啊等等，对我来说美丽很大。当然，取之精华，去之糟粕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930275}, {"id": 155910, "content": "读报", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 778523}, {"id": 156678, "content": "不看直播，不约炮，不打网游，从不去夜店，不会喜欢网红(注：不是讨厌)，不追韩剧，不用外卖软件，不刷微信红包，不刷那些支付宝的福，从不看弹幕，以及微信好友控制在50以下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911890}, {"id": 155911, "content": "除了用竹片刮和不上知乎豆瓣那两条，别的全中了。2017年刚好十三岁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910525}, {"id": 156167, "content": "对科幻电影的兴趣消减了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575227}, {"id": 156679, "content": "不喜欢骚粉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907160}, {"id": 157191, "content": "女生必须会做家务会做饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912964}, {"id": 164871, "content": "不理解和异性(除了亲近的人)出去玩为什么会好玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930275}, {"id": 155912, "content": "不用微博……", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737484}, {"id": 156168, "content": "早晨起来屁股疼…", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910851}, {"id": 158728, "content": "不喜社交，追剧，尤其厌恶电子书，对网络广告有天生的免疫力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 173539}, {"id": 155913, "content": "几年没换新内衣款式", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729095}, {"id": 156169, "content": "没有信用卡？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829148}, {"id": 1